ing: 1 (3.5 ounce) package instant vanilla pudding mix
des: "Easy, creamy, and satisfying. There is NO baking to this. Blueberry pie filling may be substituted for the cherry."
ins: In a small bowl, mix together sour cream, pudding mix, and vanilla extract. Spread mixture into crust and chill until set, about 30 minutes. Top with pie filling immediately before serving.
